{"tid":2083464,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先為之真正放低咗一個人","createTime":"2020-06-28T18:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T10:53:51.000Z","uid":154012,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8f36506abe4bb37ca6244148c659908bbbe3de21","tid":2083464,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:18:45.000Z","msg":"平時忙所以無時間去諗<br />\n有時候夜晚攤係床度都會諗返起一齊嘅點滴<br />\n甚至會睇下啲相 呢啲時候<br />\n淨係會諗起同對方相處嗰陣嘅開心時光<br />\n反而無諗過同佢一齊嗰陣嘅唔開心<br />\n會好懷念 但知返唔到轉頭<br />\n想下定決心放低佢啦<br />\n係咪當我望到有關佢嘅嘢 係無咩感受嘅時候<br />\n就係代表已經放低咗"},{"pid":"91c5ef5e02acb95eb737e53b70dd83ec23001e52","tid":2083464,"uid":96135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:19:45.000Z","msg":"Haha 我都想知"},{"pid":"d285338bc22757594fbc34f0f1decd4a6330259a","tid":2083464,"uid":92299,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:21:13.000Z","msg":"唔需要放低，大家都有開心過咪算，唔使咁計較嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62a0162a6d75f16df1cb56524c21b6db06806da","tid":2083464,"uid":75013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:21:30.000Z","msg":"我都想知"},{"pid":"b152cedb3b0b58b0d075423303dfbb6994d88767","tid":2083464,"uid":27416,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:21:43.000Z","msg":"睇見呢個post 唔會諗起佢"},{"pid":"22290544780b2f5d4956a2702472beb8f533a13c","tid":2083464,"uid":154012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d285338bc22757594fbc34f0f1decd4a6330259a","tid":2083464,"uid":92299,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:21:13.000Z","msg":"唔需要放低，大家都有開心過咪算，唔使咁計較嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:21:45.000Z","msg":"未放低會唔會對下一個唔公平"},{"pid":"77c21a1d66e2d0826f74dcb2ae78b6b4fb0659cf","tid":2083464,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:26:04.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得放低咗就唔會對佢任何事有興趣<br />\n死咗都唔會關心果種或者諗返都唔再痛<br 